attributes.title: Dogbark Plays Modded Infinite Rounds
attributes.caption: We modded Rounds to never end, and things get out of hand fast...

attributes.title: Dogbark Plays Big Head Splitgate
attributes.caption: What can be more fun than running around with big heads and only getting headshots? Using only bats and fists to take each other out! This is Splitgate... The Dogbark way!
attributes.description: What can be more fun than running around with big heads and only getting headshots? Using only bats and fists to take each other out! This is Splitgate... The Dogbark way!

attributes.title: Pigeon Boys GTA Companion Piece
attributes.caption: Have you ever wondered what it would be like to play as a pigeon in GTA V? Well, our boys decided to mod GTA to play as pigeon! Of course, in order to immerse yourself within the game you have to dress up as pigeons right?

attributes.title: Modded Zombies At Chili's
attributes.caption: There is a zombie apocalypse happening, and we are hungry! Chili's is still open, so lets check it out! I'm sure those hungry zombies won't interrupt our dinner plans right? What could go wrong in Black Ops 3 Modded zombies?

attributes.title: Mario Bros. Wonder is WEIRD
attributes.caption: Super Mario Bros. Wonder has come out! You know the boys had to get together and play it for y'all! I just wonder if they will be able to work together or, more than likely, against each other.

attributes.title: DogBark Plays Party Animals
attributes.caption: The DogBark stream of the century happens now: Party Animals.
attributes.description: The DogBark stream of the century happens now: Party Animals.

attributes.title: Our Turbulent Journey to $1,000,000 Starts Here
attributes.caption: Cue the lights, get us into that chair, and lets win an imaginable million dollars. The Dog Dudes gather their minds and try to answer questions of varying categories of their choice to try and win the big million. With their powers combined, can they do it?

attributes.title: The Scariest Game is a Retail Simulator?
attributes.caption: Half greenscreen theater, half gameplay, all chaos! Michael tries to play retail sim Night of the Consumer while Trevor, Alfredo, and Joe interrupt as in-character NPCs.
attributes.description: Half greenscreen theater, half gameplay, all chaos! Michael tries to play retail sim Night of the Consumer while Trevor, Alfredo, and Joe interrupt as in-character NPCs.

attributes.title: Is Lethal Company the Best Proxy Chat Game Ever?
attributes.caption: Joe, Alfredo, and Trevor are the lucky ones and are venturing out for the greater good (of the Corporation) and trying to scavenge materials at old buildings on planets to make a buck or two. Only thing is...they're not alone.

attributes.title: Hollow Knight but with Permadeath
attributes.caption: It's a special day. Joe's big adventure in to Hollow Knight begins. Only...he's starting off right in Steel Soul mode. So that means when he's dead...well he's dead. No coming back. The stakes are HIGH. My anxiety is spiked just writing this. Let's hunker down and watch how far our fellow barker, Joe, will get.

attributes.title: 10 Puzzles, 3 Players, 4 Cubes
attributes.caption: I know what you're thinking. "How can a simple puzzle game involving cubes be so complicated?". Well, It's harder than you think when it involves these guys. Let's see if they can get past the first 10 levels of Death Squared!

attributes.title: SHOVE - It's Exactly What You're Thinking
attributes.caption: SHOVE, a game where you do quite literally that. Try to be the last one on the stage at the end and win! Maps are filled with power ups to add to the chaos, like some good dynamite, MEGA shoves, and more!

attributes.title: Are We Closer to $1,000,000 Yet?
attributes.caption: The road to a million dollars continues as our boys continue to try to work their way up. Getting to a million seems oh so far away, but maybe this time things will be different! Let's see if changing the themes will help!
